name: TezoTubbie V2 Purple
description:
This is the 2nd Version of the Purple Tezotubbie born on Hic Et Nunc. Improving their pixels as they mature. 2/2 editions available for each.  

TezoTubbies is a creation of pixel art made with Tezos in mind and love at hand. The initial variation is 1/1 and the second 2/2, with each subsequent variation increasing in editions until the 5th version. Hoping to grow and improve this project alongside our blockchain.
